msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Live TV, everywhere"
msgstr "Teilifís bheo, i ngach áit"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "Watch your favorite programs on Kodi. Channels delivers a unified experience across all your TVs, devices, and streaming platforms."
msgstr "Féach ar do chláir is fearr leat ar Kodi. Soláthraíonn Channels eispéireas aontaithe ar fud do theilifíseáin, do ghléasanna agus d’ardáin sruthú go léir."

